SELECT
  TOP 100 *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gsksynapsestorage/synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.gso/dim_sales_force.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (


USER_ID VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        SF_SOURCE_USER_AID VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        USER_NAME VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        FIRST_NAME VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        NAME VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        LAST_NAME VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        COUNTRY VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        STATE_PROVINCE VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        CITY VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        POSTAL_CODE VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        ACTIVE_IND VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,

        NOME_GR VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        TERRITORIO_GD VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        TERRITORIO_GR VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,

        AREA VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,

        REGION VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        STATE VARCHAR(1000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
        
) AS ROW
